        <isViewedAsPlainText>false</isViewedAsPlainText>
        <text>&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;Hi &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;{!FirstName}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;Thanks for completing your consent form. This email is just to confirm we’ve received it and it will now be stored securely, in line with our data protection policy.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;If you have any questions or wish to change your permissions, you can contact us via:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;mailto:uk.info@recyclinglives.org&quot; rel=&quot;noopener noreferrer&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;uk.info@recyclinglives.org&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;If you believe you’ve received this in error, please contact us as soon as possible:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;mailto:uk.info@recyclinglives.org&quot; rel=&quot;noopener noreferrer&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;uk.info@recyclinglives.org&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;Thank you.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;Recycling Lives Charity &amp;amp; Social Enterprise&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Your Form&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;First Name: {!$Record.First_Name__c}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;Last Name: {!$Record.Last_Name__c}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;Email Address: {!$Record.Email_Address__c}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;Type of Participant: {!$Record.Type_of_Participant__c}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;Please read the following carefully before completing and submitting this form:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);&quot;&gt;Thank you for agreeing to be interviewed, photographed and/or filmed. Sharing your experience of working with Recycling Lives Charity helps us to demonstrate our impact and sustain our work. We aim to ensure that any materials are used in accordance with your wishes.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);&quot;&gt;Please read the following carefully and sign and date this form:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);&quot;&gt;1. I confirm I am happy for my case study/testimonial to be used for:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);&quot;&gt;Website: {!$Record.Website__c}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);&quot;&gt;Social media (Twitter, LinkedIn): {!$Record.Social_Media_Twitter_LinkedIn__c}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);&quot;&gt;Printed promotional materials (such as annual reports, recruitment materials or booklets): {!$Record.Printed_Promotional_Materials__c}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);&quot;&gt;Digital promotional materials (such as e-newsletters): {!$Record.Digital_Promotional_Materials__c}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);&quot;&gt;Local press: {!$Record.Local_Press__c}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);&quot;&gt;National press: {!$Record.National_Press__c}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);&quot;&gt;Industry or trade press: {!$Record.Industry_Or_Trade_Press__c}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);&quot;&gt;NB: Case studies/testimonials of those supported through our rehabilitation, residential or volunteering programmes use first names only.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);&quot;&gt;2. I confirm I am happy for my image - in photo(s) and/or video(s) - to be used for:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248); font-size: 12px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;Website: {!$Record.Website2__c}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248); font-size: 12px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;Social media (Twitter, LinkedIn): {!$Record.Social_Media_Twitter_LinkedIn2__c}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248); font-size: 12px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;Printed promotional materials (such as annual reports, recruitment materials or booklets): {!$Record.Printed_Promotional_Materials2__c}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248); font-size: 12px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;Digital promotional materials (such as e-newsletters): {!$Record.Digital_Promotional_Materials2__c}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248); font-size: 12px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;Local press: {!$Record.Local_Press2__c}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248); font-size: 12px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;National press: {!$Record.National_Press2__c}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248); font-size: 12px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;Industry or trade press: {!$Record.National_Press2__c}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);&quot;&gt;3. Third party data sharing&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);&quot;&gt;I confirm I am happy for my case study/testimonial and/or image to be shared with:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);&quot;&gt;Funding bodies (such as within tenders, proposals or funding applications): {!$Record.Funding_Bodies__c}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);&quot;&gt;Businesses (such as within proposal documents to develop partnerships or secure donations): {!$Record.Businesses__c}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);&quot;&gt;Support partners (such as support services we wish to partner with): {!$Record.Support_Partners__c}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);&quot;&gt;FareShare UK – our partner to deliver the Food Redistribution Centre: {!$Record.FareShare_UK__c}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;Your rights&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;You have the right to request to see a copy of the information we hold about you and to withdraw your consent, make corrections or deletions of the content we have of you. You can ask Recycling Lives Charity to stop using your images, videos, and case studies at any time by calling us on 01772 654321 or emailing &lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;mailto:uk.info@recyclinglives.org&quot; rel=&quot;noopener noreferrer&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;uk.info@recyclinglives.org&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;, in which case it will not be used in future publications but may continue to appear in publications already in circulation. Consent lasts for two years. We may get in touch with you to renew usage rights.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;If you have any questions relating to data protection, please contact:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;mailto:uk.info@recyclinglives.org&quot; rel=&quot;noopener noreferrer&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;uk.info@recyclinglives.org&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;Find out how we are committed to protecting your data:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.recyclinglives.org/privacy-policy/&quot; rel=&quot;noopener noreferrer&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;www.recyclinglives.org/privacy-policy/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;Date: {!$Record.Date_Submitted__c}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</text>
